      "en": "The retained sources do not establish a universal processing time. For study stays longer than six months, the consular page states that the visa is valid for one year and the student must apply for a Foreigner Identity Card within one month of entry.",
      "zh-Hans": "保留的来源没有确认统一的处理时间。对于超过六个月的学习停留，领事页面说明签证有效期为一年，学生必须在入境后一个月内申请外国人身份证。"
